PROBLEM QUESTION :-TAKING INPUT FROM USER TO CHECK WEATHER A GIVEN NUMBER IS ODD OR EVEN USING if- else loop in JAVA 

LOGIC:- 
STEP 1 - FIRST WE TAKE INPUT FROM USER 
STEP2- if entered number is divisible by 2 then it is EVEN 
       if not then ODD 
       

CODE :-

import java. util.Scanner;
public class OddEven{  
public static void main(String[] args) {
Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
System.out.println("ENTER THE VALUE OF INTEGER");
    int a = sc.nextInt();
    //Check if the number is divisible by 2 or not  
    if(a%2==0){  
        System.out.println("even number");  
    }else{  
        System.out.println("odd number");  
    }  
}  
}  

OUTPUT OF THIS PROGRAM 
ENTER THE VALUE OF INTEGER
35
odd number

